description:
◣◥  Vauxhall Parkour Youth Classes!

🤸‍♂️🏃‍♀️🧗‍♂️ Vauxhall's Ultimate Parkour Playground: Join Our Awesome Youth Class for Ages 10-14! 

👋 Hey London youth aged 10-14! Are you ready to take your parkour skills to the next level? 🤸‍♂️💪 Then join our exciting youth parkour class in Vauxhall! 🎉 

Our expert instructors will teach you how to navigate obstacles like a pro, with techniques like vaults, jumps, and swings! 🏃‍♀️🧗‍♂️ Not only will you build strength and agility, but you'll also make new friends and have a blast while doing it. 😎 So why wait? Book now and become a parkour superstar!


--- Class Details ---

🗓️ Every Sunday
⏰ 10:45am to 12pm
👩 Ages 10 to 14.
📍 Vauxhall, London
